Modol, like Roldán and Bayona with experience in urban planning, sees the proposal as an "intellectual challenge" that carries "some dangers".
Dangers as a result of the "uncertainty that the design of a public space entails today" according to the experiences of the 1980s, which had their "swan song" in the field of the forum.
